flowRoot.flowPara: GNOME brings companies, volunteers, professionals and non-profits together from around the world. GUADEC is an annual event organized to gather all members of the GNOME community In 2013, GUADEC brought together 250 people from the North and South America, Europe and Asia.
GUADEC 2015 will take place in Gothenburg, Sweden.
We'll come together to meet people we’ve been working with via chat rooms and mailing lists, to make connections and network, to visit old friend and meet new ones.
Do you want to help make this happen?
The conference is organized by volunteers, and we invest a big part of our budget in travel assistance for students and members of the GNOME Foundation. Both volunteers and corporate sponsors
